pullRequest.body:
The cofinality file is currently a hodgepodge of different results and definitions. We split it as follows:

* Regular and inaccessible cardinals are moved to `SetTheory.Cardinal.Regular`. This file will also be used to define singular cardinals in the near future.
* The infinite pigeonhole principle gets its own file.

It would've been nice to move ordinal fundamental sequences as well, but they're currently (unnecessarily) used to prove some results on cofinality. A future refactor #19698 will take care of this.
